_sText:
I began making this map with out the intention of finishing, but after making the ground and water i got inspired and finished it.

its a really fun map, that is very straight forward.

the maps gameplay for me was great, plenty of cover, i made sure there is no spawn killing (90% sure), sniper towers and house hideout. 

its got all the ingredient for a great fight yard map....ENJOY!

And don't be afraid to say anything about it, likes dislikes anything. Although i wont be changing this map (final version) i will take your comments in consideration for my next map which will come soon.
